snippet.title: Backpacker 3.DMO ◄ Royal Phoenix Gaming
snippet.description:
Spelet finns bl.a. som collection på Discshop: https://www.discshop.se/spel/pc/backpacker_3_collection/P57067

This is Backpacker 3, a Swedish game, by developer and publisher Pan Vision. Check out their website at: http://www.panvision.com/

The concept is to this series is to show the "first" 5 min of the demo and nothing more of less, the reason is basically while we don't have so much time to record the full gameplay and to make it even for everyone we decided to go for the first impression idea, enjoy.

#backpacker #demogameplay #rpxnetwork
